# Needs_Action Folder

Items that require active processing by AI agents.

## Example: Email Response Required

```markdown
---
type: email
from: client@example.com
subject: Invoice Request
received: 2026-03-09T10:30:00Z
priority: high
status: pending
assigned_to: email_agent
---

## Email Content

Can you please send me the invoice for last month?

## Suggested Actions

- [ ] Generate invoice #1234
- [ ] Reply with invoice attached
- [ ] Archive email after sending
```

## Example: Social Media Comment

```markdown
---
type: facebook_comment
post_id: 1101488969704000_123456
from: John Doe
comment: Great service! Do you offer discounts for startups?
received: 2026-03-09T14:20:00Z
priority: normal
status: pending
assigned_to: social_media_agent
---

## Suggested Actions

- [ ] Draft friendly response
- [ ] Check if discount policy applies
- [ ] Post response after approval
```
